Please report ANY bugs and missing languages to batterylife1.8.x@rbtdigital.com. Thank you very much! [b2] Several fixes. [b3] Possible fix for iOS 8 crash. General bug fixes. [b4] iOS 8 bug fixes. [b12] Fix for b11. [b13] Bugfixes. [b14] Bugfixes. [b15] Bugfixes. [b16] Fixed settings not opening. Fixed ads not disappearing. General bugfixes. [b17] Quick crashfix. [b18] Bugfixes & updated translations. Automatically saves battery stat history without the need to open the app. [b19] Bugfixes. [b20] Fixes for iOS 9 and 10. [b21] Fixed temperature unit in app. Changed App Icon to distinguish from the App Store version. [b22] Bugfixes. Should be close to final now.
